My name is Miri, and my pronouns are they/them. I'm dammmithardison#2135 on discord. I just started a gofundme to get a hysterectomy. You can donate directly here or reblog this post to spread the word
Some quick points: 
1) If I've reblogged something that was written by a terf let me know and I'll delete it. 
2) I'm agender, quoioromantic, and asexual. I don't think the word queer is a slur. If you don't like that, fuck off. 
3) I'm a Jew living in Israel who supports the existence of a Jewish state. I'm an Israeli  citizen. If you don't like that, fuck off. 
4) FARTs (Feminist Appropriating Reactionary Transphobes), exclusionists, aphobes, antisemites, anti-Zionists, and other bigots- Fuck. Off.
